with him about that.

35:27.709 --> 35:29.042
I mean, I know you guys
make different rules...

35:29.077 --> 35:30.077
Get off the bar.

35:30.078 --> 35:31.111
Okay.

35:31.145 --> 35:33.547
You are stronger than you look.

35:33.581 --> 35:37.150
- Blake, please come back.
- Don't talk to me.

35:37.185 --> 35:39.519
What is the matter with you?
Karen and Kyle?

35:39.554 --> 35:41.154
You could not find
two better friends.

35:41.189 --> 35:42.356
They have done nothing
but love you.

35:42.390 --> 35:44.891
Well, yes.

35:44.926 --> 35:47.361
