is in love with me,

35:47.395 --> 35:50.397
and it is not the one
that I wanted.

35:56.971 --> 35:58.272
Are you okay?

35:58.306 --> 36:00.941
- Uh, Ana, thank you, I...
- Don't worry about it.

36:00.975 --> 36:02.743
