36:18.259 --> 36:19.860
I'll do it tomorrow,
when he's sober

36:19.894 --> 36:21.128
and when I've had a chance
to calm down.

36:21.162 --> 36:23.130
No, you don't wait
until tomorrow.

36:23.164 --> 36:25.465
If you wait until then,
you'll lose your courage.

36:25.500 --> 36:27.234
Do it now.

36:27.268 --> 36:29.870
Thank you, Karen.

36:29.904 --> 36:32.940
You're right.

