and it's a risk

37:04.739 --> 37:06.473
I just can't afford to take.

37:06.507 --> 37:08.575
- Okay.
- I'm sorry, Derek.

37:08.610 --> 37:10.444
I know how much
you put into this.

37:10.478 --> 37:13.947
- Thanks, darling.
- Okay.

37:16.117 --> 37:17.985
